timing_extract...validation_dir(25.10)  timing_extract...validation_dir(25.10)

Name
       timing_extract_model_exhaustive_validation_dir

Syntax
       timing_extract_model_exhaustive_validation_dir <string>

       Default: " "

       Specifies  the output directory where the additional validation reports
       generated during ETM Extremity Validation  (but  not  generated  during
       normal validation) will be written.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

